rim product INT and \n2018/9 rerun with Jan -June \n2020 extension \n \nSusan Kay, Robert \nMcEwan, David Ford \nMarina Tonani \n \n  \nQUID for NWS MFC Products  \nNWSHELF_MULTIYEAR_BIO_004_011 \nRef: \nDate: \nIssue: \nCMEMS-NWS-QUID-004-011 \n24 February 2021 \n5.1 \n \n \n3 \n \nTABLE OF CONTENTS \nTable of contents ................................................................................................................................................. 3 \nList of Data Tables ............................................................................................................................................... 4 \nList of Figures ...................................................................................................................................................... 5 \nI Executive summary ..................................................................................................................................... 7 \nI.1 Products covered by this document ........................................................................................................... 7 \nI.2 Summary of the results .............................................................................................................................. 7 \nI.3 Estimated Accuracy Numbers ..................................................................................................................... 8 \nII Production system description .................................................................................................................... 9 \nIII Validation framework ............................................................................................................................... 13 \nIV Validation results ...................................................................................................................................... 16 \nIV.1 Chlorophyll-a .............................................................................